hopobject.body: Could you tell me the dialing code for ? unimedcg.com.br As well as the much-lauded W Verbier, this winter also sees the completion of two long-awaited lift connections that make it much easier to explore the whole of the 4 Valleys. One accesses the heart of the Bruson ski area – up till now, an insider’s secret among locals. This winter it will be just two seamless gondola rides from Verbier. A second high-speed gondola transforms the link between the 4 Valleys resorts of Siviez and Nendaz.
